description: The trees have been cleared out here to create space for a large bamboo changing hut with a brightly lettered sign propped up before it.  A trio of unlit torches rest beside the hut, while a narrow footpath is worn into the soil in the direction of the nearby lagoon.
title: [Saewehna Jungle, Small Clearing]
location: the environs of the Saewehna Lagoon
